Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.20,1:05:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.93,1:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}要停下来吗
